sub_title: Project Manager at European Space Agency
summary: I hold a double master in space technologies and engineering with a specialization in optronics from Polytech. Since 2000, I worked successively for different economic actors as the European Southern Observatory (ESO), Airbus Defence & Space (ADS), the Centre National de la Recherche Scientifique (CNRS), LuxSpace (OHB group), the Luxembourg agency for Innovation & Research (Luxinnovation) and the Luxembourg Space Agency (LSA). Now, I am working for the European Space Agency (ESTEC) as Project Manager.
